Package smarthome.persistence.datamodel.mapper

Class SensorDataModelMapper

java.lang.Object
smarthome.persistence.datamodel.mapper.SensorDataModelMapper
@Component public class SensorDataModelMapper extends Object
This class is responsible for mapping between SensorDataModel and Sensor domain entities. It uses a SensorFactory object to create Sensor domain entities.
